-- India's Idea Cellular sets price range for share sale - termsheet
-- By Himank Sharma
-- Thu Jun 05, 2014 08:16AM EDT
-- None



MUMBAI, June 5 (Reuters) - India's Idea Cellular Ltd <IDEA.NS> set an indicative price range of 131-136.35 rupees for its share sale to raise up to 30 billion rupees ($505.5 million), according to a termsheet seen by Reuters.

The company had set the floor price for the sale at 136.98 rupees. [ID:nL3N0OM2WJ]